      "rationale": "Simulated NIH compared against experimental measurements at 5 operating points. Mean absolute relative error of 8.4% achieved at the chosen solver configuration (Lagrangian time-step multiplier 0.02, threshold shear stress 150 Pa). All individual point errors remain below 13%. Acceptance criterion of 15% MARE is satisfied. Parameter values are documented in the validation narrative only; no structured binding exists in this package."
