      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA GCBP, a centrifugal pump geometry representative of the CPB device class. Operating envelope (flow rates and rotational speeds) overlaps with the COU envelope. Turbulence model (SST k-omega) and hemolysis model (power-law) are identical between validation and COU simulations. Relevance is judged adequate for MRL 2."
