      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for rotating machinery flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al. form) selected based on literature prevalence and available calibration data. Sensitivity of NIH to model form evaluated by comparison with Lagrangian stress-accumulation approach; difference of 6.2% within acceptable range for MRL 2."
    },
